Design and implement web service (REST) application for distance calculation:
Ј	Database holds two entities:
o	City
І	Name
І	Latitude
І	Longitude
o	Distance
І	From city
І	To city
І	Distance
Ј	Application should make it possible to calculate the distance in two ways:
o	УCrowflightФ (straight distance) between cities. Lookup formula for distance calculation on the sphere in the internet.
o	Lookup distance between two cities via Уdistance matrixФ (distance table in the database)
Ј	API has 3 endpoints:
o	List of all cities in the DB. Fields:
І	ID
І	Name
o	Calculate distance
І	Input:
Ј	Calculation Type: <Crowflight, Distance Matrix, All>
Ј	From City: <List of cities>
Ј	To City: <List of Cities>
І	Output:
Ј	Results: all distance calculation results as requested
o	Upload data to the DB. Uploads XML file with cities and distances into the application. Application parses it and stores it into the database.
І	Input:
Ј	Multipart/form-data form submission with single УFileФ input.
І	Output:
Ј	HTTP response code 200 without body
